  <ul>
    <li><a href="/docs/architecture">Architecture</a> — kernel and FCP driver model</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/secrets">Secrets</a> — how the kernel resolves <code>&dollar;VARIABLE</code> references</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/pins">Capability Pins</a> — how pins restrict MCP tool access</li>
    <li><a href="/docs/commands">Commands</a> — <code>ostk mcp list</code> and <code>ostk mcp call</code></li>
  </ul>
</DocsLayout>
